### 25. First Query - Establish Context
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is a CRG?",
  "user_id": "multi-turn-user",
  "session_id": "session-abc123"
}

### 26. Follow-up Query - Use Session Context
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What does it do?",
  "user_id": "multi-turn-user",
  "session_id": "session-abc123"
}

### 27. Retrieve Conversation History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/multi-turn-user/session-abc123
